\begin_layout Itemize
These qualified edgels are compared with each other one and assigned a weight
 based on how many other edgels are candidates to be "radially opposite"
 (i.e.
 have a gradient direction that is almost opposite from self, and orthogonality
 of other pixel offset direction with respect to self gradient, and vice
 versa).
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Classify radEdgels into groups defined by a common gradient angle direction.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


